copyFields string List of from-to fields (123,456),(124,457) that we can use to generate the fields in the SIGN record (only valid for isSignedReport)
itemList string <optional>
 (optional) list of items to use in the report. By default all categories are used
url string <optional>
 (optional) url to generate in the filter
resturl string <optional>
 (optional) REST url to generate in the filter
format string <optional>
 (optional) format - html (default), pdf, docx, odt, xml, zipdocx, zippdf or package (from 2.2), or mf (since 2.3)
filter string <optional>
 (optional) specify a comma-delimited filter list. Can be negative filters (with minus before)
useOld number <optional>
 (optional) ask to use the old report engine (pre 1.11) if set to 1.
atDate string <optional>
 (optional) generates the report at that date - format is ISO8601 like atDate=2018-05-30T14 - 48 - 27.223Z
options * <optional>
 Override http request option.
